From 198fd099deb2aa3eb5597ab560bcfc1407918abf Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sri Vidya Gunturi <sgunturi@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Sat, 19 Jul 2025 00:32:38 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] ath12k-wifi7-extn: Add support to compile ath12k-wifi7 extensions code for ath12k-wifi7

Add support to compile the ath12k-wifi extension files using the
ath12k/wifi7/Makefile.
The qcn_extns/Makefile is linked to ath12k/wifi7/Makefile.

Add this patch in the qca-driver-extns/patches folder.
Copy and apply this patch into the backports for building
the extension code.

Signed-off-by: Sri Vidya Gunturi <sgunturi@qti.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Venkateswara Swamy Bandaru <vbandaru@qti.qualcomm.com>

---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/Makefile | 5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/Makefile b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/Makefile
index daaeb4b..0220bd0 100644
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/Makefile
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/Makefile
@@ -25,4 +25,6 @@ ath12k_wifi7-y += core.o \
 		  dp_mon2.o \
 		  dp_mon1_filter.o
 
+ath12k_wifi7-$(CPTCFG_QCN_EXTN) += qcn_extns/wifi7_hw_extn.o
+
 ath12k_wifi7-$(CPTCFG_ATH12K_AHB) += ahb.o
-- 
2.34.1

